# Keep the Docker build context small and reproducible: never copy installed deps, build outputs,
# caches, VCS metadata, secrets, or local tooling artifacts into the image. The builder stage runs a
# clean `pnpm install --frozen-lockfile` from the committed lockfile, so node_modules must NOT leak in.

# Dependencies (reinstalled inside the builder from the frozen lockfile)
**/node_modules

# Build outputs & generated artifacts
**/dist
**/build
**/storybook-static
**/.vite
**/.next
**/coverage
playwright-report
test-results

# Caches & tooling
**/.turbo
.git
.github
.husky
.vscode
.changeset
.playwright-mcp

# Secrets & local env (never bake into an image)
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
*.log

# Docs & compose files not needed at build time
docker/observability
docker-compose*.yml
**/Dockerfile
.dockerignore
